{
  "name": "RPlog_Lunch_With_a_Legend",
  "title": "Lunch with a Legend",
  "summary": "The smuggler Axel Vrichten brings his ship Boomstick to dock aboard the Litigator over Etti IV for a meeting with the Maffi lieutenant Gren Delede. Over a meal in the wardroom, the two businessmen size each other up, trading dry remarks about a tactless pirate who once offered Axel substandard spice as a bargaining chip. Axel produces a high-tech datacard and plays back a recording of a sensitive conversation, which Delede asks to copy for the crimelord Eson. Delede explains that as a member of the family, Axel is expected to help broaden the organization's business connections, while Axel declines to commit until he sees firsthand how they operate. The frank, no-small-talk exchange leaves both men with a wary mutual respect and the groundwork laid for future dealings.",
